<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
  <meta name="description" content="Sam Bruton — Resume"/>
  <title>Sam Bruton - Developer</title>

  <link rel="icon" href="./assets/favicon.ico"/>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./assets/main.css"/>
</head>

<body>

	<main id="top" class="wrap">
		<div class="hero reveal">
			<div class="headline">
				<div class="flex mb">
					<div>
						<p class="kicker">Website & Application Developer</p>
						<h1>
							Bringing ideas to life through code
						</h1>
						<p class="sub">
							Great at building start-up web applications that are user-friendly, efficient, and scalable.
							<br/>Passionate about creating seamless user experiences and delivering high-quality solutions that meet
							business goals.
						</p>

						<div class="meta" role="list" aria-label="Quick facts">
							<div class="chip" role="listitem">Based in: <strong><a
											href="https://utctime.info/timezone/GMT/" target="_blank">GMT</a></strong></div>
							<div class="chip" role="listitem">Focus: <strong>End-to-end</strong></div>
							<div class="chip" role="listitem">Tech stack: <strong>MacOS, Webstorm, MX
								Pro</strong></div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="logo align-right">
						<img src="./assets/sb-logo.svg" alt="sam bruton frontend engineering logo"/>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="portfolio">
					<div>
						<h4>2025</h4>
						<ul>
							<li>In Plane Site – Artist's website (client)</li>
							<li>Cavu – Airport software contract</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div>
						<h4>2026</h4>
						<ul>
							<li>The labs – Company website (client)</li>
							<li>Lib tech – Node api project (client)</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div>
						<h4>Future</h4>
						<ul>
							<li>Rapider ltd – Food company (client)</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="grid">
			<!-- LEFT: Main narrative -->
			<div class="stack">
				<section id="work" class="reveal">
					<div class="section-title">
						<h2>Work that shipped</h2>
						<span>Experience</span>
					</div>

					<div class="stack">
						<div class="card">
							<div class="row">
								<div>
									<p class="role">Frontend Development - Cavu</p>
									<p class="where">Customer Team • enhancing the post-purchase customer journey</p>
								</div>
								<div class="when">2024 — 2026</div>
							</div>
							<ul>
								<li>Enhancing the airport passenger journey by building new features and fixing bugs</li>
								<li>Improving the codebase - documentation, knowledge-sharing and Vue 3 upgrades</li>
								<li>Craft an authentication flow using Auth0 for customer service order mgmt</li>
								<li>Maintaining domain ownership within monorepos - whitelabel and saas applications</li>
							</ul>
						</div>

						<div class="card">
							<div class="row">
								<div>
									<p class="role">Frontend Development - The labs</p>
									<p class="where">Marketing • designed &amp; built agency website</p>
								</div>
								<div class="when">2026</div>
							</div>
							<ul>
								<li>A newly formed company wanted a website designed and built</li>
								<li>Collaboration with company founders' on an agreed design using figma tools</li>
								<li>Needed to comply to WCAG and be quick to load</li>
							</ul>
						</div>

						<div class="card">
							<div class="row">
								<div>
									<p class="role">API Development - Lib tech</p>
									<p class="where">Tech • Designed &amp; built api endpoints</p>
								</div>
								<div class="when">2026</div>
							</div>
							<ul>
								<li>Api built with express node server</li>
								<li>Handles submission of form data, authentication and data retrieval</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</section>

				<section id="craft" class="reveal">
					<div class="section-title">
						<h2>How I like to build</h2>
						<span>Skills · Projects · Principles</span>
					</div>

					<div class="stack">
						<div class="card">
							<div class="row">
								<div>
									<p class="role">Signature strengths</p>
									<p class="where">A short list of “things you’re known for” (3–6 bullets)</p>
								</div>
								<div class="when">Now</div>
							</div>
							<ul>
								<li>Example: “Design-system thinking with practical guardrails.”</li>
								<li>Example: “Testing habits that keep refactors boring (in a good way).”</li>
								<li>Example: “Performance and accessibility as defaults, not afterthoughts.”</li>
							</ul>
						</div>

						<div class="card">
							<div class="row">
								<div>
									<p class="role">Selected builds</p>
									<p class="where">Add 2–4 projects with a one-line purpose + what you contributed</p>
								</div>
								<div class="when">Highlights</div>
							</div>
							<ul>
								<li><strong>Project Name</strong> — what it does · what you improved · (link)</li>
								<li><strong>Project Name</strong> — what it does · what you improved · (link)</li>
								<li><strong>Project Name</strong> — what it does · what you improved · (link)</li>
							</ul>
						</div>

						<div class="card">
							<div class="row">
								<div>
									<p class="role">Tools I reach for</p>
									<p class="where">Keep this short; only include what you truly use</p>
								</div>
								<div class="when">Stack</div>
							</div>
							<ul>
								<li>Frontend: (e.g., Vue/Nuxt, React, TypeScript)</li>
								<li>Testing: (e.g., Vitest/Jest, Playwright/Cypress)</li>
								<li>Platform: (e.g., AWS, Terraform, CI/CD)</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</section>

				<section id="involvements" class="reveal">
					<div class="section-title">
						<h2>Outside the commit log</h2>
						<span>Involvements</span>
					</div>

					<div class="stack">
						<div class="card">
							<div class="row">
								<div>
									<p class="role">Community / Mentorship / Speaking</p>
									<p class="where">Add what you do beyond your day job</p>
								</div>
								<div class="when">Ongoing</div>
							</div>
							<ul>
								<li>Security champions, guilds, meetups, mentoring, reviews, writing.</li>
								<li>Talk/panel/workshop (topic + where + link).</li>
							</ul>
						</div>

						<div class="card">
							<div class="row">
								<div>
									<p class="role">Learning lane</p>
									<p class="where">What you’re currently exploring and why it matters to you</p>
								</div>
								<div class="when">This year</div>
							</div>
							<ul>
								<li>Example: “React patterns + accessibility-friendly UI primitives.”</li>
								<li>Example: “Technical leadership: scope changes, ownership, and shipping confidently.”</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</section>
			</div>

			<!-- RIGHT: Quick scan -->
			<div class="stack">
				<section class="reveal" aria-label="Quick scan">
					<div class="section-title">
						<h2>Quick scan</h2>
						<span>At a glance</span>
					</div>

					<div class="stack">
						<div class="mini">
							<h3>Core skills</h3>
							<div class="pillrow">
								<span class="pill">TypeScript</span>
								<span class="pill">Vue / Nuxt</span>
								<span class="pill">React</span>
								<span class="pill">Design Systems</span>
								<span class="pill">Testing</span>
								<span class="pill">Accessibility</span>
								<span class="pill">Performance</span>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="mini">
							<h3>What I optimize for</h3>
							<div class="two-col">
								<span class="pill">Clarity</span>
								<span class="pill">Consistency</span>
								<span class="pill">Maintainability</span>
								<span class="pill">Speed</span>
								<span class="pill">Reliability</span>
								<span class="pill">Simplicity</span>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="mini">
							<h3>Signals</h3>
							<ul>
								<li>Replace with a short “proof” line (metrics, scope, scale).</li>
								<li>Replace with another credibility nugget (ownership, leadership).</li>
								<li>Replace with one more (users served, revenue impacted, latency improved).</li>
							</ul>
						</div>

						<div class="mini" id="contact">
							<h3>Contact</h3>
							<p style="margin:0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6;">
								Email: <a href="mailto:you@example.com">you@example.com</a><br/>
								LinkedIn: <a href="#">linkedin.com/in/your-handle</a><br/>
								GitHub: <a href="#">github.com/your-handle</a><br/>
								Location: <span style="color: rgba(255,255,255,.78);">United Kingdom</span>
							</p>

							<div class="sep"></div>

							<a class="btn" href="#" style="width:100%; justify-content:center;">
								Book a chat ↘
							</a>
							<p style="margin:10px 0 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px;">
								Tip: replace “Book a chat” with Calendly or a simple mailto.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</section>

				<section class="reveal" aria-label="Small details">
					<div class="section-title">
						<h2>Small details</h2>
						<span>Extras</span>
					</div>
					<div class="mini">
						<h3>Writing / Notes</h3>
						<ul>
							<li><strong>Post title</strong> — one sentence summary · (link)</li>
							<li><strong>Post title</strong> — one sentence summary · (link)</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="mini" style="margin-top: 12px;">
						<h3>Certifications</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Certification name — issuer (year)</li>
							<li>Certification name — issuer (year)</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</section>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>

	<footer class="mb ">
		<img
			src="assets/qrcode-ig-sb.svg"
			alt="Scan QR code for my instagram"
			width="200"
			height="200"
		/>
	</footer>

	<script src="./assets/theme.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
